data.description: Lovely 2 story open floor plan home with many updates! This home features a living room and dining room with arched doorways and beautiful crown molding. The kitchen features lots of cabinets, huge pantry and a large island with breakfast bar and eating area. Keeping room is open to the kitchen with a gorgeous fireplace and French doors to deck and patio. Also, on main level you will find a powder room and a full size laundry room and coat closet. The stairs and master has original hardwood floors. Carpet replaced within past 6 months. Upstairs features a huge master suite with sitting area and 2 HUGE walk in closets.Very spacious master bath with jetted tub, double sinks,separate shower and toilet. 3 more spacious bedrooms and closets. (one currently being used as office) Hallway is wide and has a sitting nook and huge double closet.2nd Bath has double sink vanity w separate tub and toilet. 1 HVAC unit 2014, 1 is 5 yrs.,Roof 2014,Hot water Heater 3 yrs old, main level flooring 1 yr.
